  {team:'Washington',handles:['@PurpleToolbox','@HuskyAfterDark','@MontlakeMacGyver'],tag:'#GoHuskies',quips:[angle=>`Seattle forecast: rain, purple, and a 100 percent chance that ${angle}.`,angle=>`Montlake engineering has received the toolbox after hearing ${angle}.`,angle=>`The Dawgs found a coach who hears ${angle} and immediately asks for the wiring diagram.`,angle=>`If ${angle}, Washington better reinforce every outlet in Husky Stadium.`,angle=>`Purple, gold, and classified: ${angle}. Welcome to Seattle, Dusty.`]}
